      "text": "Republicans’ Big Ugly Bill gutted Americans’ healthcare and ripped food from hungry families in order to pay for a tax cut for billionaires.\n\nMore than 8 million Americans have already lost their healthcare and over 4 million Americans have lost food assistance.\n\nIn the richest",
